    <Title>Butter Chicken</Title>
    <Introduction>
        <Description Image="../Images/bc.jpg" Source="http://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1016754-butter-chicken">Butter chicken is the General Tso’s of Indian food, a great, ever-evolving, cross-continental dish found in Delhi, London, New York, Perth and most points in between.
        </Description>
    </Introduction>
